XML CALLForDSTS V4 This is a configuration for call for parts using a DXM700 with up to 40 K70 touch with 3 colors (K70DXN9T2GRYQ) and up to 7 DX80N9DSTS (DSTS). This configuration enables the DXM and the above devices to work as a call for parts application, where a touch on the button (usually station) will start a call on the DSTS displays (usually forklifts or supervisors). Please check the callForDSTS.pdf document for detailed info.
This XML requires the Call For parts DSTS Script file (callForDSTS_V4.sb) and is only to be used on the DXM700 or newer devices.
